sketch.compiler.passes.lowering

Class GetExprType

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENullVisitor
      • sketch.compiler.passes.lowering.GetExprType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEVisitor

    public class GetExprType
extends FENullVisitor
    Visitor that returns the type of an expression. This needs to be created with a symbol table to help resolve the types of variables. All of the visitor methods return Types.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    David Maze <dmaze@cag.lcs.mit.edu>
